terday%20and%20is%20recovering%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1752098683024220632%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BInitial%20results%20show%20promising%20neuron%20spike%20detection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20product%20is%20called%20Telepathy%2C%20Musk%20said%20in%20a%20follow-up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1752119586470949056%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20device%20%26quot%3Benables%20control%20of%20your%20phone%20or%20computer%2C%20and%20through%20them%20almost%20any%20device%2C%20just%20by%20thinking.%20Initial%20users%20will%20be%20those%20who%20have%20lost%20the%20use%20of%20their%20limbs.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImagine%20if%20Stephen%20Hawking%20could%20communicate%20faster%20than%20a%20speed%20typist%20or%20auctioneer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20the%20goal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20previously%20said%20the%20Neuralink%20device%20would%20record%20and%20stimulate%20brain%20activity%2C%20acting%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BFitbit%20in%20your%20skull%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20claimed%20the%20implant%20would%20eventually%20%26quot%3Bsolve%26quot%3B%20conditions%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-said-neuralink-could-solve-autism-and-schizophrenia-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eautism%20and%20schizophrenia%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Hilary%20Brueck%20reported%20in%202091%20that%20neuroscientists%20believe%20Neuralink%20won't%20likely%20be%20able%20to%20%26quot%3Bsolve%26quot%3B%20mental%20health%20conditions%20or%20change%20the%20developmental%20architecture%20of%20the%20brain%20when%20it%20is%20impacted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-neuralink-wont-solve-autism-schizophrenia-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediseases%20like%20Alzheimer's%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20the%20technology%20may%20be%20effective%20at%20stimulating%20electrodes%2C%20thereby%20helping%20paralyzed%20patients%20achieve%20better%20mobility%20or%20helping%20blind%20patients%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Neuralink%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EYears%20in%20the%20making%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20CEO%20has%20been%20promising%20that%20Neuralink%20would%20soon%20begin%20testing%20on%20humans%20since%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20initially%20rejected%20Neuralink's%20request%20for%20approval%20to%20test%20its%20brain%20chips%20in%20humans%20last%20March%2C%20citing%20concerns%20that%20it%20could%20overheat%20or%20move%20in%20the%20brain%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Fneuralink-musk-fda%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EReuters%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20Approval%20was%20ultimately%20granted%20in%20May%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20approval%20prompted%20thousands%20of%20prospective%20patients%20to%20sign%20up%20as%20volunteers%20to%20have%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterest-neuralink-human-trial-patient-elon-musk-brain-implant-report-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskull%20removed%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20implant%20inserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20company%20began%20recruiting%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-apply-for-neuralink-human-trial-study-requirements-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efirst%20human%20trial%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20September%2C%20Neuralink%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%