hark%20mauled%20a%20woman%20as%20she%20swam%20in%20Sydney%20Harbour%20in%20a%20gory%20attack%20that%20left%20her%20in%20hospital%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bserious%26quot%3B%20leg%20injury%2C%20officials%20and%20media%20said%20Tuesday.%20The%20predator%20struck%20Monday%20evening%20as%20the%20woman%20swam%20off%20a%20wharf%20at%20Elizabeth%20Bay%2C%20less%20than%20two%20kilometres%20(1.2%20miles)%20from%20the%20iconic%20Sydney%20Opera%20House%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20suffered%20a%20%26quot%3Bserious%20injury%20to%20her%20right%20leg%26quot%3B%2C%20New%20South%20Wales%20police%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20first%20shark%20attack%20in%20Sydney%20Harbour%20since%202009%2C%20when%20an%20Australian%20navy%20diver%20fought%20off%20a%20bull%20shark%20that%20bit%20him%20in%20the%20arm%20and%20leg%20in%20Woolloomooloo%20Bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeighbours%20rushed%20to%20help%20the%20Elizabeth%20Bay%20victim%2C%20the%20Sydney%20Morning%20Herald%20said%2C%20identifying%20her%20as%2029-year-old%20Lauren%20O'Neill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20quoted%20one%20resident%20who%20heard%20her%20%26quot%3Bsoft%20yell%26quot%3B%20for%20help%20from%20his%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20trying%20to%20climb%20in%20and%20behind%20her%20was%20her%20leg%2C%20which%20was%20completely%20open%20and%20full%20of%20dark%20red%20blood%20behind%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20resident%20Michael%20Porter%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20surreal.%20We%20have%20always%20been%20worried%20and%20known%20about%20sharks%20in%20the%20harbour...%20it's%20only%20now%20that%20it%20feels%20very%20real.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20vet%20living%20nearby%20applied%20a%20tourniquet%2C%20the%20paper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20swam%20out%20to%20the%20boat%20and%20on%20her%20way%20back%20she%20got%20bitten%20by%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was%2C%20a%20bull%20shark%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20witness%20t