the%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20alliance%20hold%20a%20combined%20total%20of%2020%20votes%2C%20posing%20a%20formidable%20challenge%20to%20the%20BJP's%2015%20votes%2C%20which%20includes%2014%20councillors%20and%20the%20additional%20vote%20of%20MP%20Kirron%20Kher.%20The%20magic%20number%20for%20victory%20stands%20at%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20process%20has%20not%20been%20without%20its%20share%20of%20legal%20hurdles.%20The%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%2C%20in%20its%20January%2024%20order%2C%20directed%20the%20Chandigarh%20administration%20to%20conduct%20the%20mayoral%20polls%20today%2C%20quashing%20the%20earlier%20postponement%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bunreasonable%2C%20unjustified%2C%20and%20arbitrary.%26quot%3B%20The%20court%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%2C%20prohibiting%20councillors%20from%20being%20accompanied%20by%20supporters%20or%20security%20personnel%20from%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20parties%20involved%20have%20adopted%20a%20cautious%20approach%2C%20keeping%20their%20councillors%20on%20the%20move%20before%20the%20polling%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP-Congress%20alliance%20has%20strategically%20nominated%20candidates%20for%20the%20various%20positions.%20Kuldeep%20Kumar%2C%20representing%20the%20AAP%2C%20is%20contesting%20for%20the%20mayoral%20post%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20is%20fielding%20candidates%20for%20senior%20deputy%20mayor%20and%20deputy%20mayor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP-Congress%20alliance%20seeks%20to%20break%20the%20BJP's%20eight-year%20rule%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20at%2010%20am.%20The%20Congress%20abstained%20from%20voting%20in%202022%20and%202023%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20BJP's%20victory%20in%20those%20polls.%20The%20election%20process%20for%20the%20mayor's%20position%20is%20conducted%20through%20a%20secret%20ballot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20year's%20elections%2C%20the%20mayor's%20seat%20is%20reserved%20for%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20category%2C%20with%20Manoj%20Sonkar%20representing%20the%20BJP%20and%20Mr%20Kumar%20from%20the%20AAP%20as%20the%20contenders.%20The%20senior%20deputy%20mayor%20post%20will%20see%20Kuljeet%20Sandhu%20of%20the%20BJP%20facing%20off%20against%20Congress's%20Gurpreet%20Singh%20Gabi%2C%20while%20the%20deputy%20mayor%20position%20will%20be%20contested%20between%20BJP's%20Rajinder%20Sharma%20and%20Congress's%20Nirmala%20Devi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706578440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-03%2Fqeklno2_voting-generic-up-pti-650_650x400_07_March_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandigarh-mayor-polls-today-as-bjp-faces-aap-congress-alliance-4957512%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chandigarh%20mayoral%20election%20will%20take%20place%20today%2C%20pitting%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20against%20an%20alliance%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20and%20the%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandigarh-mayor-polls-today-as-bjp-faces-aap-congress-alliance-4957512%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandigarh-mayor-polls-today-as-bjp-faces-aap-congress-alliance-4957512%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandigarh-mayor-polls-today-as-bjp-faces-aap-congress-alliance-4957512%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20Says%201st%20Human%20Patient%20Has%20Received%20Neuralink's%20Brain%20Implant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20his%20Neuralink%20startup%20had%20installed%20a%20brain%20implant%20in%20its%20first%20human%20patient%20with%20%26quot%3Bpromising%26quot%3B%20initial%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20neurotechnology%20company%20co-founded%20by%20Musk%20in%202016%20aims%20to%20build%20direct%20communication%20channels%20between%20the%20brain%20and%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ambition%20is%20to%20supercharge%20human%20capabilities%2C%20treat%20neurological%20disorders%20like%20ALS%20or%20Parkinson's%2C%20and%20maybe%20one%20day%20achieve%20a%20symbiotic%20relationship%20between%20humans%20and%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20human%20received%20an%20implant%20from%20Neuralink%20yesterday%20and%20is%20recovering%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInitial%20results%20show%20promising%20neuron%20spike%20detection%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20human%20received%20an%20implant%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fneuralink%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Neuralink%3C%2Fa%3E%20yesterday%20and%20is%20recovering%20well.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnInitial%20results%20show%20promising%20neuron%20spike%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1752098683024220632%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2029%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20start-up%20last%20year%20said%20it%20won%20approval%20from%20US%20regulators%20to%20test%20its%20brain%20implants%20in%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeuralink's%20technology%20will%20mainly%20work%20through%20an%20implant%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BLink%26quot%3B%20--%20a%20device%20about%20the%20size%20of%20five%20stacked%20coins%20that%20is%20placed%20inside%20the%20human%20brain%20through%20invasive%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20company%20Pitchbook%2C%20last%20year%20California-based%20Neuralink%20had%20more%20than%20400%20employees%20and%20has%20raised%20at%20least%20%24363%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20wins%20most%20of%20the%20headlines%2C%20Musk%20is%20hardly%20alone%20in%20trying%20to%20make%20advances%20in%20the%20field%2C%20which%20is%20officially%20known%20as%20brain-machine%20or%20brain-computer%20interface%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHit%20with%20delays%2C%20the%20tycoon%20had%20reportedly%20reached%20out%20to%20join%20forces%20with%20implant%20developer%20Synchron%20about%20a%20potential%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Neuralink's%20Link%2C%20its%20implant%20version%20does%20not%20require%20cutting%20into%20the%20skull%20to%20install%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Australia-based%20Synchron%20implanted%20its%20first%20device%20in%20a%20US%20patient%20in%20July%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706578260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-03%2Fs2ku2tf8_elon-musk-reuters_625x300_25_March_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-says-neuralink-has-implanted-first-brain-chip-in-human-patient-4957314%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20his%20Neuralink%20startup%20had%20installed%20a%20brain%20implant%20in%20its%20first%20human%20patient%20with%20%26quot%3Bpromising%26quot%3B%20initial%20results.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-says-neuralink-has-implanted-first-brain-chip-in-human-patient-4957314%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-says-neuralink-has-implanted-first-brain-chip-in-human-patient-4957314%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-says-neuralink-has-implanted-first-brain-chip-in-human-patient-4957314%2Famp%2F