A1706570720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FHOHH_104_Unit_00042R.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235890639%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Oliver%20Jackson-Cohen%E2%80%99s%20string%20of%20Netflix%20hits%20includes%202018%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Haunting%20of%20Hill%20House%E2%80%9D%20and%202020%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Haunting%20of%20Bly%20Manor%2C%E2%80%9D%20two%20Mike%20Flanagan-created%20horror%20series%20that%20garnered%20the%2037-year-old%20actor%20a%20global%20popularity%20he%E2%80%99d%20never%20seen%20prior%20to%20starring%20in%20Netflix%20originals.%20He%20parlayed%20the%20success%20of%20these%20series%20into%20a%20film%20career%20that%20spanned%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Zack%20Sharf%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fnetflix-famous-oliver-jackson-cohen-movie-star-longevity-1235890639%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fnetflix-famous-oliver-jackson-cohen-movie-star-longevity-1235890639%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fnetflix-famous-oliver-jackson-cohen-movie-star-longevity-1235890639%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2220-Year-Old%20Kills%20Friend%20Over%20%26quot%3BUnnatural%26quot%3B%20Sex%20Demand%2C%20Arrested%3A%20Delhi%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2020-year-old%20boy%20killed%20his%20friend%20after%20he%20was%20allegedly%20forced%20to%20have%20unnatural%20sex%2C%20Delhi%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDCP%20North%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Meena%20said%20on%20Monday%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20January%2019%2C%20a%20PCR%20call%20was%20received%20at%20Kashmere%20Gate%20police%20station.%20The%20caller%20stated%20that%20a%20body%20was%20lying%20in%20an%20isolated%20place%20in%20DDA%20Park%2C%20Mori%20Gate%2C%20and%20his%20face%20was%20crushed.%20The%20police%20found%20that%20an%20unknown%20body%20was%20lying%20unconscious%20in%20an%20isolated%20place%20in%20DDA%20Park%2C%20Mori%20Gate%2C%20Delhi%2C%20with%20blood%20on%20his%20mouth%20and%20a%20cut%20mark%20above%20his%20eye%20and%20blood%20was%20scattered%20around%20the%20body.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crime%20team%20of%20North%20District%20and%20the%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20(FSL)%20team%20were%20called%20to%20the%20spot%2C%20and%20the%20crime%20scene%20was%20inspected%20by%20both%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20spot%20inspection%2C%20body%20was%20shifted%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20where%20he%20was%20declared%20'brought%20dead'%20by%20the%20doctor.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20body%20was%20shifted%20and%20preserved%20at%20Mortuary%20'Subzi%20Mandi'.%20Accordingly%2C%20a%20case%20u%2Fs%20302%20IPC%20was%20registered%20at%20PS%20Kashmere%20Gate%2C%20and%20the%20investigation%20was%20taken%20up%20to%20trace%20the%20culprit%2C%26quot%3B%20DCP%20Meena%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20investigation%2C%20the%20team%20analysed%20more%20than%2050%20CCTV%20cameras%20near%20Khoya%20Mandi%2C%20Mori%20Gate%20of%20Kashmere%20Gate%20PS%2C%20but%20no%20clue%20was%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20intelligence%20was%20deployed%20to%20identify%20the%20victim%2C%20and%20inquiry%20was%20conducted%20with%20over%20100%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20was%20identified%20as%20Pramod%20Kumar%20Shukla%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Village%20Rudurpura%2C%20District%20Jalon%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20He%20was%20working%20at%20Khoya%20Mandi%20in%20the%20shop%20of%20Rakesh%20Tomar%20and%20was%20residing%20in%20Rain%20Basera%2C%20situated%20at%20Mori%20Gate%20near%20Khoya%20Mandi%2C%20DCP%20Meena%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Mobile%20Equipment%20Identity%20(IMEI)%20number%20of%20the%20mobile%20phone%20of%20the%20victim%20was%20obtained%2C%20and%20the%20IMEI%20search%20report%20was%20analysed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20detailed%20analysis%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20one%20mobile%20number%2C%20which%20was%20occasionally%20used%2C%20pertained%20to%20Rajesh%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Ghosai%20Chausa%2C%20Madhepura%2C%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20investigation%2C%20one%20person%20came%20forward%20and%20stated%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20last%20seen%20with%20Rajesh.%20It%20was%20also%20established%20that%20the%20victim%20Pramod%20Kumar%20Shukla%20and%20Rajesh%20were%20friends%20and%20lived%20together%20in%20Rain%20Basera%2C%20situated%20near%20Khoya%20Mandi%20at%20Mori%20Gate%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20fight%20took%20place%20between%20Rajesh%20and%20the%20victim%20Pramod%20Kumar%20Shukla%20on%20January%2017%20at%20DDA%20Park%2C%20Mori%20Gate%2C%20Delhi.%20After%20that%2C%20efforts%20were%20made%20to%20trace%20Rajesh%20to%20verify%20the%20facts%20and%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20Rajesh%20had%20left%20the%20area%20on%20January%2017%20and%20gone%20to%20an%20unknown%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20basis%20of%20technical%20surveillance%2C%20the%20mobile%20number%20of%20Rajesh%20was%20obtained%2C%20and%20after%20a%20detailed%20analysis%20of%20CDR%20and%20the%20location%20of%20said%20mobile%20number%2C%20he%20was%20apprehended%20from%20Patna%2C%20Bihar%2C%20on%20January%2026%20and%20thereafter%2C%20he%20was%20brought%20to%20Kashmere%20Gate%20police%20station%20and%20interrogated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interrogation%2C%20the%20accused%2C%20Rajesh%20Kumar%2C%20confessed%20that%20the%20victim%20Pramod%20Kumar%20Shukla%20was%20his%20friend%20and%20used%20to%20pressure%20him%20to%20have%20unnatural%20sex%20with%20him%2C%20which%20forced%20him%20to%20his%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2017%2C%20he%20along%20with%20the%20victim%20was%20drinking%20beer%20at%20an%20isolated%20place%20in%20DDA%20Park%2C%20behind%20Khoya%20Mandi.%20The%20victim%20Shukla%20started%20pressuring%20him%20to%20have%20