ghtRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20Iranian%20operative%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20hiring%20Hells%20Angels%20for%20assassinations%20in%20the%20US%2C%20DOJ%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20suspects%20allegedly%20conspired%20to%20hire%20biker%20group%20members%20to%20murder%20two%20Maryland%20residents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDOJ%20said%20the%20Iranian%20agent%20employs%20his%20network%20to%20target%20Iranian%20dissidents%20and%20activists.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Iranian%20drug%20trafficker%20with%20ties%20to%20its%20spy%20agency%20has%20been%20charged%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20with%20hiring%20members%20of%20the%20Hells%20Angels%20biker%20group%20to%20carry%20out%20an%20assassination%20on%20American%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDOJ%20unsealed%20the%20charges%20on%20Monday%2C%20alleging%20the%20Iranian%20operative%2C%20Naji%20Sharifi%20Zindashti%2C%20along%20with%20two%20Canadian%20nationals%20identified%20as%20Hells%20Angels%20members%2C%20Damion%20Patrick%20John%20Ryan%20and%20Adam%20Richard%20Pearson%2C%20conspired%20in%20a%20murder-for-hire%20scheme%20to%20kill%20two%20people%20in%20Maryland%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20defected%20from%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20are%20said%20to%20have%20conspired%20between%20December%202020%20through%20March%202021%2C%20with%20Zindashti%20using%20encrypted%20messaging%20to%20recruit%20agents%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20US%20and%20carry%20out%20the%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20alleged%2C%20Mr.%20Zindashti%20and%20his%20team%20of%20gunmen%2C%20including%20a%20Minnesota%20resident%2C%20used%20an%20encrypted%20messaging%20service%20to%20orchestrate%20an%20assassination%20plot%20against%20two%20individuals%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20US%20Attorney%20Andrew%20Luger%20for%20the%20District%20of%20Minnesota.%20%26quot%3BThanks%20to%20the%20skilled%20work%20of%20federal%20prosecutors%20and%20law%20enforcement%20agents%2C%20this%20murder-for-hire%