to%20go%20to%20Ayodhya%20for%20harmony%20and%20for%20the%20country.%20The%20fatwa%20was%20issued%20yesterday%20but%20I%20had%20been%20receiving%20threat%20calls%20since%20the%20evening%20of%20January%2022%2C%26quot%3B%20Ilyasi%20told%20ANI%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Islamic%20cleric%20also%20claimed%20that%20he%20has%20been%20facing%20protests%20and%20receiving%20threatening%20calls%20since%20he%20visited%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20recorded%20a%20few%20calls%20wherein%20the%20callers%20gave%20me%20life%20threats...Those%20who%20love%20me%2C%20love%20the%20nation%20will%20support%20me.%20Those%20who%20hate%20me%20for%20attending%20the%20ceremony%20should%20perhaps%20go%20to%20Pakistan.%20I%20have%20given%20a%20message%20of%20love%3B%20I%20did%20not%20do%20any%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20he%20would%20neither%20apologize%20nor%20resign%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20can%20do%20whatever%20they%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20January%2022%2C%20Dr%20Imam%20Umer%20Ahmed%20Ilyasi%20attended%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20said%20that%20his%20job%20is%20to%20spread%20the%20message%20of%20love%20and%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20face%20of%20new%20India.%20Our%20biggest%20religion%20is%20humanity.%20For%20us%2C%20the%20nation%20is%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20was%20unveiled%20at%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20ceremony%20after%20the%20hour-long%20rituals%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20who%20led%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERSS%20Chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Governor%20Anandiben%20Patel%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20were%20also%20present%20inside%20the%20sanctorum%20during%20the%20rituals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%