Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20Bal%20Mukund%20Acharya%20had%20visited%20the%20government%20school%20in%20the%20Walled%20City's%20Gangapol%20area%20during%20the%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%2C%20where%20he%20apparently%20questioned%20the%20dress%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20and%20their%20guardians%20who%20held%20protests%20today%2C%20said%20MLA%20from%20Jaipur's%20Hawa%20Mahal%20and%20asked%20why%20some%20students%20were%20wearing%20hijab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20asked%20us%20to%20raise%20religious%20slogans%20and%20when%20some%20girls%20remained%20silent%2C%20he%20said%20they%20were%20instructed%20to%20do%20so.%20He%20also%20said%20wearing%20hijab%20in%20school%20is%20not%20allowed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20of%20the%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protesting%20students%20left%20after%20a%20compromise%20was%20worked%20out%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Acharya%20later%20released%20a%20video%20clarifying%20his%20position.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20asked%20the%20principal%20if%20they%20have%20two%20different%20dress%20codes.%20When%20a%20Republic%20Day%20function%20or%20any%20government%20function%20is%20held%2C%20is%20there%20a%20different%20dress%20code%3F%20At%20this%20rate%2C%20even%20our%20children%20will%20turn%20up%20in%20lehenga%20chunni%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20MLA%20from%20Kishanpol%2C%20Amin%20Kagazi%2C%20accused%20Mr%20Acharya%20of%20destroying%20the%20amity%20and%20communal%20harmony%20of%20the%20Walled%20City.%20%26quot%3BIf%20no%20action%20is%20taken%20by%20February%202%2C%20the%20protests%20will%20begin%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20minister%20Kirori%20Lal%20Meena%20joined%20issue%2C%20claiming%20that%20hijab%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bsymbol%20of%20slavery%26quot%3B%20brought%20in%20by%20the%20Mughals.%20%26quot%3BHijab%20is%20not%20allowed%20in%20some%20Islamic%20nations.%20It%20should%20not%20happen%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Bal%20Mukund%20Acharya%20has%20set%20off%20a%20controversy.%20After%20winning%20the%20election%20last%20month%2C%20he%20was%20seen%20roaming%20the%20streets%20asking%20for%20action%20against%20illegal%20butcher%20shops.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20hijab%20issue%20had%20rocked%20Karnataka%20for%20over%20two%20years.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20under%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20B%20Bommai%20had%20banned%20headscarves%20in%20educational%20institutes%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20massive%20row.%20The%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20had%20upheld%20the%20ban%2C%20saying%20that%20wearing%20a%20hijab%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20an%20essential%20religious%20practice%20of%20Islam%26quot%3B%20but%20added%20that%20educational%20institutes%20can%20decide%20the%20dress%20code%20for%20all%20their%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20coming%20to%20power%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20has%20announced%20that%20people%20can%20%26quot%3Beat%20and%20wear%20what%20they%20liked%26quot%3B%2C%20raising%20expectation%20of%20a%20revocation%20of%20the%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHijab%20ban%20isn't%20there%20any%20more.%20(Women)%20can%20wear%20hijab%20and%20go%20anywhere.%20I%20have%20directed%20to%20withdraw%20the%20(ban)%20order.%20How%20you%20dress%20and%20what%20you%20eat%20is%20your%20choice.%20Why%20should%20I%20obstruct%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20following%20massive%20protests%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20government%20order%20to%20lift%20the%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706551680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-03%2Fjevllej4_karnataka-hijab-exams-ndtv_625x300_28_March_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Four-children-can-come-in-lehenga-bjp-mla-triggers-hijab-row-in-rajasthan-4956144%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20hijab%20controve