arrer%20Fighter%2C%20directed%20by%20Siddharth%20Anand%2C%20made%20a%20dazzling%20entry%20into%20the%20box%20office%2C%20crossing%20the%20coveted%20Rs%20100%20crore%20mark%20within%20its%20first%20four%20days%20of%20release.%20However%2C%20the%20movie%20has%20nosedived%20on%20Monday%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20the%20film's%20sustainability%20at%20the%20box%20office%20in%20the%20upcoming%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Ffighter-box-office-collection-day-5-hrithik-roshan-and-deepika-padukone-starrer-nosedives-on-monday-to-earn-rs-8-crore%2Farticleshow%2F107239906.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stop%20Mentioning%20Caste%2C%20Religion%20Of%20Litigants%20In%20Cases%3A%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20practice%20of%20mentioning%20caste%20or%20religion%20of%20litigants%20in%20court%20cases%20must%20be%20shunned%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20while%20directing%20its%20registry%20and%20all%20other%20courts%20to%20stop%20it%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20Ahsanuddin%20Amanullah%20directed%20all%20high%20courts%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20caste%20or%20religion%20of%20a%20litigant%20does%20not%20appear%20in%20the%20memo%20of%20parties%20in%20any%20petition%20filed%20before%20High%20Courts%20or%20subordinate%20courts%20under%20their%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20no%20reason%20for%20mentioning%20the%20caste%2Freligion%20of%20any%20litigant%20either%20before%20this%20Court%20or%20the%20courts%20below.%20Such%20a%20practice%20is%20to%20be%20shunned%20and%20must%20be%20ceased%20forthwith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20therefore%20deemed%20appropriate%20to%20pass%20a%20general%20order%20directing%20that%20henceforth%20the%20caste%20or%20religion%20of%20parties%20shall%20not%20be%20mentioned%20in%20the%20memo%20of%20parties%20of%20a%20petition%2Fproceeding%20filed%20before%20this%20Court%2C%20irrespective%20of%20whether%20any%20such%20details%20have%20been%20furnished%20before%20the%20courts%20below%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20passed%20the%20order%20while%20allowing%20a%20transfer%20petition%20in%20a%20marital%20dispute%20pending%20before%20a%20family%20court%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20expressed%20surprise%20that%20the%20caste%20of%20both%20the%20husband%20and%20wife%20was%20mentioned%20in%20the%20memo%20of%20the%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20for%20the%20petitioner%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20if%20the%20memo%20of%20parties%20as%20filed%20before%20the%20courts%20below%20is%20changed%20in%20any%20manner%2C%20the%20Registry%20raises%20an%20objection%2C%20and%20in%20the%20present%20case%2C%20as%20the%20caste%20of%20both%20the%20parties%20was%20mentioned%20before%20the%20court%20below%2C%20he%20had%20no%20option%20but%20to%20mention%20their%20caste%20in%20the%20transfer%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20directed%20that%20its%20order%20shall%20be%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Bar%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Registry%20for%20immediate%20compliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20copy%20of%20this%20order%20shall%20be%20placed%20before%20the%20Registrar%20concerned%20for%20perusal%20and%20for%20circulation%20to%20the%20Registrar%20Generals%20of%20all%20the%20High%20Courts%20for%20strict%20compliance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706550060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%