ick-that-scream-love%2Fphotostory%2F107239119.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lalu%20Yadav%20Questioned%20For%2010%20Hours%20By%20Central%20Agency%20In%20Land-For-Jobs%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20chief%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20has%20left%20the%C2%A0Enforcement%20Directorate%20agency%20office%20in%20Patna%20after%20he%20was%20questioned%20for%20nearly%20ten%20hours%20in%20the%20central%20agency's%20money%20laundering%20probe%20into%20the%20alleged%20land-for-jobs%20scam.%20The%20RJD%20patriarch%20was%20accompanied%20by%20his%20daughter%20Misa%20Bharti%2C%20also%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20when%20he%20entered%20the%20probe%20agency's%20office%20around%2011.05%20AM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav's%20questioning%20came%20a%20day%20after%20JDU%20president%20and%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20ditched%20the%20grand%20alliance%20in%20the%20state%2C%20in%20which%20the%20RJD%20is%20the%20largest%20constituent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav's%20party%20has%20targeted%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20over%20the%20questioning.%20RJD%20leader%20Manoj%20Jha%20said%20that%20the%20actions%20of%20central%20agencies%20will%20go%20on%20till%20the%20next%20general%20elections%20are%20concluded.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20an%20ED%20summons%2C%20but%20a%20BJP%20summons...%20This%20will%20go%20on%20till%202024%2C%20till%20then%20please%20do%20not%20call%20it%20ED%20summons...%20Why%20should%20we%20be%20scared%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMisa%20Bharti%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20actions%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20ED%20against%20her%20father%20reflects%20that%20the%20central%20government%20is%20%26quot%3Bafraid%26quot%3B%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20scam%20pertains%20to%20the%20period%20when%20Mr%20Yadav%20was%20the%20railway%20minister%20in%20the%20UPA-1%20government.%20It%20is%20alleged%20that%20from%202004%20to%202009%2C%20several%20people%20were%20appointed%20to%20Group%20%26quot%3BD%26quot%3B%20positions%20in%20various%20zones%20of%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20for%20which%20they%20transferred%20their%20land%20to%20the%20family%20members%20of%20the%20then%20railway%20minister%20Lalu%20Yadav%20and%20a%20linked%20company%20named%20AK%20Infosystems%20Private%20Limited%20as%20bribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20or%20ED%20had%20earlier%20said%20AK%20Infosystems%20Private%20Limited%20is%20allegedly%20a%20%26quot%3Bbeneficiary%20company%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20case%20and%20its%20registered%20address%20in%20south%20Delhi's%20New%20Friends%20Colony%20was%20being%20used%20by%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20-%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20son%20and%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20laundering%20case%2C%20filed%20under%20the%20criminal%20sections%20of%20the%20PMLA%2C%20stems%20from%20a%20complaint%20lodged%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20that%20filed%20a%20charge%20sheet%20in%20this%20case%20earlier.%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20Rabri%20Devi%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20were%20granted%20bail%20by%20a%20trial%20court%20in%20October%20last%20year%20in%20the%20CBI%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20ED%20filed%20its%20first%20charge%20sheet%20in%20the%20case%20and%20named%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav's%20wife%20and%20former%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Rabri%20Devi%20and%20their%20MP%20daughter%20Misa%20Bharti%20among%20others%20as%20accused.%20Mr%20Yadav's%20another%20daughter%20Hema%20Yadav%20was%20also%20named%20in%20the%20charge%20sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20probe%20agency%20seized%20assets%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%20six%20crore%20%C2%A0belonging%20to%20Rabri%20Devi%2C%20Misa%20Bharti%20and%20linked%20companies%20as%20part%20of%20this%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706545440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3