6quot%3Bclosing%20conditions%26quot%3B%20were%20not%20satisfied%20after%20two%20years%20of%20negotiations.%20Neither%20Sony%20nor%20Zee%20made%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20termination%20notice%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReviewed%20by%20Reuters%2C%20Sony's%20notice%20said%20Zee%20had%20%26quot%3Bfailed%20to%20take%20commercially%20reasonable%26quot%3B%20efforts%20to%20meet%20some%20financial%20thresholds%2C%20including%20with%20regards%20to%20cash%20availability%2C%20while%20a%20%26quot%3Black%20of%20commercial%20prudence%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Indian%20network%20contributed%20to%20its%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2062-page%20notice%2C%20Sony%20said%20several%20breaches%20of%20the%20merger%20agreement%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20remediable%20and%20any%20further%20attempts%20to%20mutually%20discuss%20would%20be%20an%20empty%20formality%2C%20especially%20given%20...%20plain%20denial%20(by%20Zee)%20and%20failure%20to%20provide%20a%20proposal%20to%20protect%26quot%3B%20Sony's%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20breaches%20committed%20by%20Zee%20are%20not%20'procedural%20or%20technical'%20in%20nature%20and%20will%20have%20a%20substantive%20impact%20on%20the%20transactions%2C%26quot%3B%20Sony%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZee%20responded%20privately%20to%20Sony%20a%20day%20later%2C%20on%20Jan.%2023%2C%20saying%20it%20denied%20all%20Sony's%20allegations%2C%20adding%20the%20Japanese%20company's%20demand%20for%20a%20termination%20fee%20of%20%2490%20million%20was%20%26quot%3Blegally%20untenable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20termination%20was%20%26quot%3Beffected%20in%20bad%20faith%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bis%20wrongful%2C%20bad%20in%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Zee%20wrote%20in%20its%20letter%2C%20which%20asked%20Sony%20to%20withdraw%20its%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Zee%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment%2C%20while%20Sony%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Reuters%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZee's%20shares%20have%20fallen%20about%2030%25%20s