be%20destroyed%20after%20their%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20has%20stirred%20an%20emotive%20debate%20in%20the%20war-torn%20country%20with%20Ukraine%20still%20suffering%20heavy%20losses%20nearly%20two%20years%20after%20the%20Russian%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20parliamentary%20speaker%20Olena%20Kondratyuk%20said%20lawmakers%20will%20introduce%20%26quot%3Ban%20amendment%20today%20that%20will%20cancel%20the%20postmortem%20disposal%20of%20biomaterials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20wave%20of%20public%20indignation%20will%20hopefully%20convince%20the%20deputies%20to%20vote%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kondratyuk%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Fatherland%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyer%20Olena%20Babych%20sparked%20a%20wide%20debate%20last%20week%20by%20revealing%20the%20dilemma%20of%20a%20woman%20whose%20husband%20had%20frozen%20his%20sperm%20before%20he%20was%20killed%20at%20the%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20had%20to%20break%20it%20to%20her%20client%20that%20she%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20use%20the%20sperm%20in%20a%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20explain%20to%20a%20grief-stricken%20woman...%20that%20while%20her%20husband%20was%20defending%20the%20state%20and%20died%2C%20our%20lawmakers%20literally%20deprived%20him%20of%20the%20right%20to%20be%20a%20father%20after%20his%20death%3F%26quot%3B%20Babych%20wrote%20on%20Facebook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20law%20passed%20last%20year%20allows%20Ukrainian%20troops%20to%20freeze%20their%20sperm%20or%20eggs%20for%20free%20in%20case%20they%20are%20injured%20in%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20also%20said%20they%20would%20be%20destroyed%20if%20the%20fighter%20dies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20ministry%20later%20released%20a%20statement%20saying%20that%20reproductive%20clinics%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20dispose%20of%20frozen%20biomaterial%20of%20fallen%20soldiers%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20legislative