Cp%3ECapital%20expenditure%20(plan%20vs.%20non%20plan)%20also%20follows%20a%20different%20pattern%20with%20actual%20and%20budgeted%20expenditure%20mapping%20throughout%20the%20years%2C%20but%2C%20for%20revenue%20accounts%2C%20when%20we%20look%20at%20which%20of%20it%20was%20planned%20and%20unplanned%2C%20there%20is%20still%20a%20wide%20divergence%20in%20trend%20across%20the%20years-indicating%20a%20large%20increase%20in%20non-plan%20expenditure%20overheads%20(especially%20prior%20to%202015).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAimless%20capex-bloat%20coming%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20key%20upward%20mobility-based%20welfare%20spending%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20fuel%20a%20bloated%20capex-driven%20fiscal%20budget%20and%20fiscally%20afford%20this%20amidst%20weaker%20than%20anticipated%20revenues%2C%20the%20last%20few%20Union%20Budgets%20not%20only%20trimmed%20social%20spending%20but%20did%20so%20in%20a%20year%20when%20capital%20expenditure%20rose%20substantially.%20The%20Modi%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Feconomy%2Famid-indias-silent-fiscal-crisis-and-fragile-federalism-16th-finance-commission-has-an-uphill-task%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3Ehas%20also%20been%20responsible%20for%20squeezing%20state%20governments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20inhibiting%20their%20fiscal%20space%20for%20supporting%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20significant%20reduction%20in%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20social%20spending%20was%20observed%20in%20the%20budgeted%20allocation%20for%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20scheme%2C%20seen%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29160415%2FB6.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D