3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-wont-get-more-than-20-seats-in-2025-prashant-kishors-big-prediction-101706436357404.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kishor%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-Amit%20Shah%20duo%20could%20also%20be%20given%20the%20%E2%80%98palturam%E2%80%99%20title%2C%20since%20they%20have%20been%20lashing%20out%20at%20Nitish%20for%20his%20alleged%20corruption%20and%20misgovernance%2C%20but%20did%20not%20hesitate%20to%20welcome%20him%20back%20into%20their%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishor%20said%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20NDA%20stint%20is%20unlikely%20to%20last.%20He%20added%20that%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20party%20will%20not%20win%20more%20than%2020%20seats%20in%20the%20next%20assembly%20elections%2C%20no%20matter%20who%20it%20is%20in%20alliance%20with%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20he%20had%20predicted%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20switch%20back%20to%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20Nitish%20Kumar%20wins%20more%20than%2020%20seats%20in%20the%20next%20Assembly%20election%2C%20I%20will%20take%20retirement%20from%20my%20work.%20Please%20write%20it%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20of%20Bihar%20will%20pay%20Nitish%20Kumar%20back%20with%20interest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20present%20Bihar%20picture%2C%20there%20are%20two%20sides.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20the%20face%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20BJP.%20On%20the%20other%2C%20there%20is%20RJD%20and%20the%20other%20parties.%20Bihar%20assembly%20election%20will%20not%20take%20place%20in%20this%20formation.%20Before%20the%20next%20Bihar%20election%2C%20there%20will%20be%20many%20dramatic%20developments.%20Within%20six%20months%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20you%20will%20see%20those%20developments%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kishor%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20follow%20my%20statements%20for%20the%20past%20year%2C%20you%20will%20find%20that%20I%20am%20the%20only%20person%20who%20has%20been%20saying%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%20can%20flip%20anytime.%20But%20today%20it%20is%20proved%20that%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20too%20can%20vie%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98palturam%E2%80%99%20moniker%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20strategist%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishor%20referred%20to%20his%20previous%20statement%20that%20if%20Nitish%20had%20continued%20in%20the%20RJD%20alliance%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20win%20even%20five%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20got%20scared%20after%20my%20prediction%20and%20left%20Mahgathbandhan.%20My%20next%20prediction%20is%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20party%20won%E2%80%99t%20get%20more%20than%2020%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20election%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Nitish%20resigned%20from%20his%20post%20as%20chief%20minister%20after%20exiting%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20rejoining%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20only%20to%20be%20sworn%20in%20again%20for%20the%20ninth%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706508014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29112459%2FPK-NK.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitishs-flip-shows-modi-shah-too-can-vie-for-palturam-moniker-prashant-kishor%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20added%20that%20Nitish's%20party%20will%20not%20win%20more%20than%2020%20seats%20in%20the%20next%20assembly%20elections%2C%20no%20matter%20who%20it%20is%20in%20alliance%20with.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitishs-flip-shows-modi-shah-too-can-vie-for-palturam-moniker-prashant-kishor%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suspended%20WFI%20Holds%20its%20Own%20'Nationals'%2C%20Leading%20to%20a%20Quandary%20for%20India's%20Wrestlers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21155114%2FEffect-38.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20community%20continues%20to%20face%20chaos%20and%20administrative%20confusion%2C%20as%20the%20suspended%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%2C%20with%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20loyalist%20Sanjay%20Singh%20at%20its%20helm%2C%20hold%20%E2%80%98senior%20nationals%E2%80%99%20in%20Pune%20despite%20its%20suspension.%20Most%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20players%2C%20however%2C%20are%20giving%20this%20tournament%20a%20miss%20and%20instead%20attending%20the%20%E2%80%98nationals%E2%80%99%20organised%20by%20the%20ad%20hoc%20committee%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Union%20sports%20minister%20early%20next%20month%2C%20in%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20was%20accused%20of%20serious%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20at%20least%20seven%20women%20wrestlers.%20While%20the%20police%20has%20failed%20to%20act%20against%20him%20and%20he%20continues%20in%20his%20position%20as%20MP%2C%20he%20was%20removed%20as%20the%20WFI%20head%20after%20prolonged%20protests%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20wrestlers.%20The%20same%20wrestlers%20had%20protested%20again%20when%20Sanjay%20Singh%20was%20elected%20the%20new%20WFI%20president%2C%20leading%20the%20sports%20ministry%20to%20suspend%20the%20WFI%20and%20appoint%20a%20new%20ad%20hoc%20panel%20to%20look%20over%20wrestling%20in%20India.%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20however%2C%20had%20claimed%20that%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fsport-others%2Fwe-do-not-recognise-this-ad-hoc-panel-or-suspension-suspended-wfi-president-sanjay-singh-9090834%2F%5C%22%3Ewould%20not%20recognise%20this%20suspension%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20line%20with%20this%20stubborn%20insistence%2C%20the%20suspended%20WFI%20has%20organised%20a%20%E2%80%98senior%20nationals%E2%80%99%20meet%20in%20Pune%20between%20January%2029%20and%2031.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fsport-others%2Fat-suspended-wfi-nationals-wrestlers-in-fix-venue-infested-by-mosquitoes-9131985%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20the%20venue%20is%20infested%20with%20mosquitoes%20and%20most%20top%20names%20across%20weight%20categories%20have%20not%20made%20an%20appearance.%20%E2%80%9CMaharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Atish%20Todkar%2C%20who%20beat%20Ravi%20Dahiya%20in%20the%20Asian%20Games%20trials%20in%20July%202023%2C%20is%20the%20only%20notable%20name%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20aren%E2%80%99t%20any%20big%20names%20in%20the%20fray%20here%20as%20Railways%20and%20Services%20aren%E2%80%99t%20coming%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20at%20the%20event%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaction%20from%20within%20the%2024%20state%20bodies%20have%20tried%20to%20send%20in%20a%20collection%20of%20wrestlers%20in%20an%20attempted%20show%20of%20strength%20in%20support%20of%20Sanjay%20Singh.%20But%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20states%2C%20barring%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Assam%20are%20also%20sending%20a%20full%20team%20to%20Jaipur%2C%20where%20the%20medal%20winners%20will%20proceed%20to%20a%20national%20camp%20and%20be%20considered%20for%20trials%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20situation%20%E2%80%93%20with%20two%20competing%20tournaments%20within%20a%20week%20of%20each%20other%20%E2%80%93%20has%20left%20wrestlers%20in%20a%20conundrum%2C%20as%20it%20is%20unclear%20which%20one%20will%20lead%20the%20way%20forward.%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%2072%20kg%20grappler%2C%20Asna%20Sareen%2C%20for%20instance%20said%20she%20be%20turning%20up%20at%20both.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20our%20state%20assoc