e-major-problem-for-biden-both-at-home-and-abroad-13058977%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Keeping%20Post%20Vacant%20For%2015%20Months%2C%20China%20May%20Appoint%20New%20Envoy%20to%20India%20Soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28214931%2FIndia-and-China.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20China%20may%20finally%20have%20a%20new%20ambassador%20in%20India%20early%20this%20year%2C%20with%20Beijing%20reportedly%20having%20selected%20a%20two-time%20envoy%20to%20fill%20the%20post%2C%20which%20has%20been%20lying%20vacant%20for%20over%2015%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20China%20has%20finalised%20one%20of%20its%20assistant%20foreign%20ministers%20posted%20at%20headquarters%20in%20Beijing%2C%20Xu%20Feihong%2C%20as%20the%20next%20ambassador%20to%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%2C%20however%2C%20no%20official%20confirmation%20from%20either%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%20or%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EXu%20is%20currently%20assistant%20minister%20for%20financial%20and%20administrative%20affairs%20in%20the%20foreign%20ministry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20side%20has%20been%20conveyed%20about%20the%20candidate%2C%20as%20per%20informed%20sources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20it%20was%20earlier%20expected%20that%20he%20could%20be%20arriving%20as%20early%20as%20around%20the%20time%20of%20the%20Spring%20Festival%20next%20month%2C%20it%20is%20uncertain%20if%20that%20timeline%20is%20feasible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EXu%E2%80%99s%20position%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mfa.gov.cn%2Fweb%2Fziliao_674904%2Fwjrw_674925%2F202102%2Ft20210218_9881048.shtml%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eassistant%20foreign%20minister%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20roughly%20equivalent%20to%20the%20rank%20of%20additional%20secretary%20in%20the%20MEA.%20Since%20the%20post%20of%20Chinese%20ambassador%20to%20India%20is%20of%20the%20vice-minister%20rank%2C%20he%20would%20need%20to%20be%20promoted%20before%20he%20comes%20to%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20previous%20two%20Chinese%20ambassadors%20to%20India%2C%20Sun%20Weidong%20and%20his%20predecessor%2C%20Lui%20Zhaohui%2C%20had%20significant%20experience%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20including%20prior%20postings%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Lu%20Yucheng%2C%20who%20preceded%20Lui%2C%20did%20not%20have%20any%20regional%20experience.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%2037%20years%20as%20a%20Chinese%20diplomat%2C%20Xu%E2%80%99s%20only%20assignment%20in%20South%20Asia%20was%20as%20ambassador%20to%20Afghanistan%20from%202010%20to%202013.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20his%20postings%20have%20been%20in%20the%20Western%20world%2C%20ranging%20from%20Finland%20to%20Australia%2C%20with%20a%20specialisation%20in%20Europe.%20His%20last%20ambassadorial%20posting%20had%20been%20in%20Romania%20from%202015%20to%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%E2%80%99s%20latest%20ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Sun%20Weidong%2C%20left%20his%20post%20in%20October%202022%20after%20three%20years%20that%20saw%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20Asian%20neighbours%20plummet%20following%20fatal%20clashes%20in%20the%20mountainous%20heights%20of%20eastern%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20April-May%202020%2C%20India%20and%20China%20have%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20military%20stand-off%20in%20the%20western%20part%20of%20their%20long%20border.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20claimed%20that%20Chinese%20troops%20had%20moved%20further%20beyond%20their%20traditional%20positions%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%2C%20resulting%20in%20multiple%20skirmishes%20with%20the%20patrolling%20teams%20of%20the%20Indian%20army.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20deadliest%20conflict%20took%20place%20on%20June%2015%2C%20when%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20engaged%20in%20a%20hand-to-hand%20fight%20at%20the%20Galwan%20valley%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20and%20at%20least%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchina-acknowledges-casualties-galwan-clash-india-army%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efour%20Chinese%20troops%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20at%20least%2020%20rounds%20of%20military-level%20talks%20and%2013%20rounds%20of%20foreign%20office-led%20discussions%20have%20been%20held%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20had%20led%20to%20disengagement%20at%20five%20friction%20points%20at%20the%20Pangong%20Tso%20lake%E2%80%99s%20north%20and%20south%20banks%2C%20patrolling%20points%2015%20and%2017A%20at%20the%20Gogra-Hot%20Springs%20area%20and%20Galwan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20ambassador%20Sun%20left%20in%202022%2C%20Demchok%20and%20Depsang%20were%20the%20remaining%20areas%20of%20stand-off.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFifteen%20months%20on%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20change%20on%20this%20front.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20maintains%20that%20the%20standoff%20will%20only%20be%20resolved%20once%20there%20is%20disengagement%20and%20de-escalation%20at%20Demchok%20and%20Depsang.%20In%20contrast%2C%20China%20asserts%20that%20the%20alteration%20in%20status%20quo%20after%20May%202020%20does%20not%20encompass%20these%20two%20areas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%20has%20repeatedly%20called%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnormalisation%E2%80%9D%20of%20ties%20and%20to%20go%20beyond%20the%20border%20dispute%2C%20but%20India%20insists%20that%20the%20stand-off%20has%20to%20be%20resolved%20first.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObservers%20interpret%20the%20prolonged%20delay%20in%20appointing%20another%20Chinese%20envoy%20to%20the%20Indian%20capital%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20holds%20a%20senior%20rank%20and%20would%20have%20enough%20takers%2C%20as%20a%20deliberate%20signal%20of%20displeasure%20from%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20border%20issue%2C%20there%20had%20been%20other%20issues%20over%20which%20Beijing%20has%20expressed%20its%20annoyance%2C%20like%20the%20financial%20investigations%20of%20major%20Chinese%20companies%20in%20India.%20China%20had%20also%20not%20been%20happy%20when%20India%20had%20turned%20the%20SCO%20summit%20into%20a%20virtual%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20president%20Xi%20Jinping%20also%20skipped%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20India%2C%20despite%20having%20gone%20to%20Indonesia%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%201962%20war%2C%20both%20countries%20exchanged%20ambassadors%20only%20after%20a%20gap%20of%2015%20years%20in%201976.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20there%20has%20usually%20been%20only%20a%20short%20gap%20of%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20at%20the%20most%20between%20ambassadors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706459298000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28214931%2FIndia-and-China.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fchina-may-appoint-new-ambassador-to-india-soon%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20has%20learnt%20that%20China%20has%20finalised%20one%20of%20its%20assistant%20foreign%20ministers%20posted%20at%20headquarters%20in%20Beijing%2C%20Xu%20Feihong%2C%20as%20the%20next%20ambassador%20to%20India.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fchina-may-appoint-new-ambassador-to-india-soon%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%2