%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Bar%20Council%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKovind%20also%20met%20Deepak%20Pandurang%20Dhavalikar%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Maharastrawadi%20Gomantak%20Party%2C%20Goa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20political%20parties%20are%20not%20in%20support%20of%20the%20proposition%2C%20seeing%20it%20as%20a%20deeply%20centralising%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20national%20parties%2C%2033%20state%20parties%20and%20seven%20registered%20unrecognised%20parties%20have%20been%20formally%20written%20to%20and%20asked%20for%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%20was%20termed%20an%20%E2%80%9Cundemocratic%E2%80%9D%20idea%20%E2%80%9Cagainst%20%5Bthe%5D%20basic%20structure%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20Constitution%E2%80%9D%20by%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20earlier%20this%20month.%20He%20said%20the%20panel%20on%20this%20must%20be%20dissolved%20and%20the%20idea%20abandoned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fone-nation-one-election-an-undemocratic-idea-against-basic-structure-of-constitution-kharge-to-kovind-panel-9117337%2F%5C%22%3Efor%20the%20sake%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Crobust%20democracy%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetail.aspx%3FPRID%3D2000148%5C%22%3Efourth%20meeting%20of%20the%20high-level%20committee%20was%20also%20held%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday%20(January%2027).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20representative%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20this%20committee%2C%20with%20Congress%20leader%20and%20MP%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20having%20refused%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20Kovind%20said%20that%20polls%20being%20held%20concurrently%20at%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20levels%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fone-nation-one-election-in-national-interest-nothing-to-do-with-any-party-ram-nath-kovind%2Farticle67557721.ece%5C%22%3Eis%20in%20the%20national%20interest%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20it%20would%20benefit%20whichever%20party%20was%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbe%20it%20BJP%20or%20Congress%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20November%2021%2C%202023%2C%20Chowdhury%20had%20called%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cparty%20agenda%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20requesting%20all%20the%20political%20parties%20to%20cooperate%20as%20this%20is%20in%20the%20national%20interest.%20No%20political%20party%20has%20got%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kovind%20told%20the%20media%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20a%20public%20notice%2C%20the%20high-level%20committee%20had%20called%20for%20suggestions%2C%20and%20said%20those%20received%20by%20January%2015%20would%20be%20taken%20up%20for%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20leader%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%2C%20who%20is%20also%20former%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%3B%20N.K.%20Singh%2C%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%3B%20Subhash%20C.%20Kashyap%2C%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general%3B%20Sanjay%20Kothari%2C%20former%20chief%20vigilance%20commissioner%20and%20Harish%20Salve%2C%20senior%20advocate%20attended%20the%20meeting%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20government%20release%20on%20the%20meeting%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20presentation%20was%20made%20before%20the%20committee%20based%20on%20the%20research%20paper%20%E2%80%98Macroeconomic%20Impact%20of%20Harmonizing%20Electoral%20Cycles%2C%20Evidences%20from%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20co-authored%20by%20N.K%20Singh%20and%20Prachi%20Mishra.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20committee%20also%20decided%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20conversation%20process%20with%20stakeholders%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20argument%20of%20%E2%80%98cost-saving%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20critiqued%20by%20the%20Congress%20already%20when%20Kharge%20wrote%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20committee%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ECI%20had%20estimated%20the%20cost%20of%20conducting%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20with%20VVPAT%20machines%20to%20be%20about%20Rs%203%2C870%20crore%20%E2%80%A6%20The%20argument%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20conducting%20elections%20is%20extremely%20high%20seems%20baseless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsidering%20elections%20are%20held%20once%20in%20five%20years%2C%20the%20expenses%20make%20up%20less%20than%200.02%25%20of%20the%20total%20Union%20budget%20for%20the%20preceding%20five%20years.%20When%20elections%20are%20held%20separately%20to%20the%20state%20assemblies%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20election%20is%20fully%20borne%20by%20the%20respective%20states.%20The%20expenses%20for%20assembly%20elections%20may%20also%20be%20a%20similar%20percentage%20of%20their%20state%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20feel%20the%20people%20will%20be%20willing%20to%20consider%20this%20small%20amount%20as%20the%20cost%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20to%20uphold%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPI(M)%20has%20also%20written%20to%20the%20committee%20registering%20its%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20objection%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98ONOE%E2%80%99%20is%20being%20%E2%80%9Csought%20to%20be%20imposed%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20consideration%20of%20the%20proposal%20itself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fcpim-calls-one-nation-one-election-inherently-anti-democratic-in-letter-to-kovind-led-panel-2839525%5C%22%3Eruns%20against%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fgovt-committee-simultaneous-elections-explained-8918921%2F%5C%22%3Ein%202015%2C%20a%20parliamentary%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20compiled%20a%20report%20on%20simultaneous%20elections%2C%20but%20the%20Congress%20at%20the%20time%20told%20the%20committee%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cimpractical%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunworkable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20called%20the%20report%20anti-democratic%20and%20unconstitutional%2C%20while%20the%20CPI%20and%20the%20NCP%20said%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20feasible%E2%80%9D.%20The%20CPI(M)%20also%20highlighted%20%E2%80%9Cpractical%20problems%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsimultaneous-elections-panel-suggestions-9096160%2F%5C%22%3EKovind-led%20committee%E2%80%99s%20terms%20of%20reference%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20is%20meant%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexamine%20and%20make%20recommendations%20for%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections%20to%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%20(Lok%20Sabha)%2C%20State%20Legislative%20Assemblies%2C%20Municipalities%20and%20Panchayats%2C%20keeping%20in%20view%20the%20existing%20framework%20under%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20and%20other%20statutory%20provisions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20purpose%2C%20it%20is%20meant%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexamine%20and%20recommend%20specific%20amendments%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201950%2C%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201951%2C%20and%20the%20rules%20made%20thereunder%20and%20any%20other%20law%20or%20rules%20which%20would%20require%20amendments%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706456127000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26110403%2FThe-Wire-56.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsimultaneous-elections-high-level-committee-holds-its-fourth-meeting%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind-led%20committee%20constituted%20late%20last%20year%2C%20without%20any%20consultation%20with%20the%20opposition%20and%20without%20their%20representation%2C%20continues%20to%20seek%20out%20legal%20opinion%20and%20build%20a%20case%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98macroeconomic%20impact%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20one%20election%20plan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsimultaneous-elections-high-level-committee-holds-its-fourth-meeting%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22More%20Clashes%20Reported%20in%20Manipur%3B%20Moreh%20Residents%20Demand%20Removal%20of%20State%20Forces%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Days%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1062725%2Fin-imphal-the-states-surrender-to-an-armed-meitei-militia-with-taliban-like-grip%5C%22%3Emeeting%20of%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20militia%20group%20with%2037%20MLAs%20and%20two%20MPs%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Manipur%2C%20at%20least%20two%20people%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20were%20killed%20on%20Saturday%20(January%2027)%20and%20several%20houses%20and%20churches%20in%20the%20Khamenlok%20area%20were%20burnt%20down%2C%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%20(ITLF)%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ITLF%2C%20which%20is%20an%20influential%20tribal%20body%20based%20in%20the%20state%2C%20alleges%20that%20the%20two%20men%20were%20safeguarding%20their%20village%20and%20were%20reportedly%20fired%20upon%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20(AR)%2C%20a%20paramilitary%20force%20controlled%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20Rifles%20is%20yet%20to%20comment%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhamenlok%20is%20a%20sensitive%20area%20and%20has%20two%20access%20points%20%E2%80%93%20one%20in%20Imphal%20and%20the%20other%20in%20Saikul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonths%20ago%2C%20when%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20attempted%20to%20visit%20the%20area%2C%20both%20Union%20and%20state%20forces%20warned%20this%20reporter%20not%20to%20visit%2C%20citing%20potential%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhamenlok%20has%20many%20churches%20and%20several%20videos%20purportedly%20show%20the%20burning%20of%20churches%20there%20and%20another%20group%20celebrating%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20members%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community%20allege%20that%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%2C%20which%20is%20a%20Meitei%20group%2C%20has%20burnt%20all%20villages%20in%20the%20Khamenlok%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20Saikul%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20morning%20at%20around%205%3A30%20am%2C%20another%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20group%20attacked%20the%20Senam%20Kom%20area%20of%20Saikul%2C%20leading%20to%20%5Ban%20exchange%20of%20fire%5D%20with%20village%20volunteers%20for%20half%20an%20hour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gunfight%20continued%20until%207%3A30%20am%20and%20the%20situation%20worsened%20in%20the%20Imphal%20East%20district%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20wrote%20to%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20regarding%20the%20alleged%20assault%20on%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20president%2C%20Keisham%20Meghachandra%2C%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F7LhsAvBhLP8%3Fsi%3Ds5B5UzTMRWsRg86J%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20four-point%20letter%20to%20Shah%2C%20Kharge%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20shocking%20incident%20has%20occurred%20despite%20the%20heavy%20presence%20of%20Central%20and%20Security%20forces%2C%20and%20intelligence%20personnel.%20Till%20date%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20action%20from%20the%20Manipur%20CM%20and%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20on%20this%20disturbing%20subversion%20of%20democratic%20processes%20by%20a%20non-state%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20shameful%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20eloquent%20silence%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Manipur%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20prevailing%20strategy%20from%20all%20important%20stakeholders%20in%20both%20the%20State%20and%20the%20Centre.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoreh%20continues%20to%20boil%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20border%20town%20of%20Moreh%20continues%20to%20boil%20nearly%20a%20month%20after%20security%20personnel%20there%20were%20ambushed%20by%20suspected%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20in%20the%20border%20town%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-kuki-zos-hold-major-sit-in-protest-demanding-restoration-of-peace-in-moreh-795258-2024-01-27%5C%22%3Estaged%20a%20sit-in%20protest%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday%20(January%2027)%20demanding%20the%20restoration%20of%20peace%20in%20the%20region.%20They%20are%20also%20demanding%20the%20removal%20of%20state%20forces%20from%20Moreh%20and%20the%20reopening%20of%20schools%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20protest%20was%20jointly%20organised%20by%20the%20Kuki%20Students%E2%80%99%20Organisation%2C%20Moreh%20Block%20and%20the%20Kuki%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Union%20for%20Human%20Rights%2C%20Moreh.%20It%20was%20also%20joined%20by%20the%20Moreh%20Private%20Schools%20Association%3B%20the%20Kuki%20Inpi%2C%20Tengnoupal%3B%20and%20the%20Hill%20Tribal%20Council%2C%20Moreh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5