te-Republic-Day%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonate%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FCelebrate-Republic-Day%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overwhelming%20burden%20of%20finances%20often%20used%20to%20cause%20Vikas%20to%20skip%20school.%20Because%2C%20even%20while%20admission%20to%20public%20schools%20is%20free%20in%20India%2C%20books%2C%20stationery%20items%20and%20school%20bags%20aren%E2%80%99t.%20As%20the%20family%20navigated%20through%20the%20financial%20crisis%2C%20these%20expenses%20would%20add%20to%20their%20woes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20easiest%20option%20was%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336586%2Fbastar-ias-officer-vinit-nandanwar-free-coaching-for-neet-jee-exam-to-tribal-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschool%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Vikas%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20not%20an%20exception.%20It%20is%20the%20ground%20reality%20of%20thousands%20of%20children%20in%20remote%20Indian%20villages%20whose%20parents%20work%20as%20farmers%20and%20labourers%2C%20earning%20just%20enough%20to%20live%20hand%20to%20mouth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBear%20in%20mind%20that%20even%20the%20%E2%80%98Rs%20150%20a%20day%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20promised%20amount%20only%20as%20long%20as%20the%20contract%20goes%20on%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20six%20months.%20The%20remainder%20of%20the%20year%20these%20farm%20labourers%20do%20not%20have%20work%20since%20there%20are%20no%20rains%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amol%20Sainwar%2C%20founder%20and%20president%20of%20Shivprabha%20Charitable%20Trust%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336276%2Fmadhura-rajvanshi-fulbright-scholar-dis