%20who%20immediately%20went%20to%20the%20police%2C%20who%20arrested%20the%20three%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20followed%20makes%20the%20tale%20harrowing.%20Going%20against%20the%20entire%20village%2C%20the%20film%20follows%20Ranjit%20from%20the%20time%20he%20first%20reports%20the%20crime%20and%20his%20journey%20over%2014%20months%20as%20he%20pursues%20justice%20and%20ensures%20that%20the%20criminals%20are%20brought%20to%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20documents%20how%20village%20elders%20expected%20Kiran%20to%20marry%20one%20of%20her%20abusers.%20A%20woman%20in%20the%20village%20is%20heard%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20could%20have%20been%20settled%20in%20the%20village.%20They%20already%20had%20sex%2C%20might%20as%20well%20get%20them%20married%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20shows%20the%20stark%20reality%20for%20many%20abused%20women%2C%20which%20is%20scary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%20and%20mindset%2C%20the%20relentless%20pursuit%20of%20justice%20in%20the%20face%20of%20pressure%20and%20intimidation%20to%20drop%20the%20case%20is%20worth%20every%20plaudit.%20Ranjit%2C%20his%20wife%20Jaganti%2C%20and%20Kiran%20remain%20unfazed.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20think%20of%20Kiran%2C%20every%20fear%20goes%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20Ranjit%20in%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRanjit%20simply%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20status%20quo%20and%2C%20because%20of%20that%2C%20showed%20us%20that%20change%20is%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pahuja%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20as%20Kiran%20turned%2018%20by%20the%20time%20the%20editing%20of%20the%20documentary%20film%20was%20completed%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20come%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20not%20wanting%20to%20remain%20hidden.%20She%20wished%20to%20encourage%20other%20survivors%20through%20her%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20film%20would%20also%20connect%20with%20many%20on%20its%20quotient%20of%20resilience%20and%20how%20we%20can%20go%20that%20extra%20mile%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20protecting%20those%20we%20love.%20On%20its%20surface%2C%20it%20may%20feel%20like%20a%20film%20from%20India%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20actually%20a%20film%20about%20what%20it%20feels%20to%20be%20a%20human.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20continues%20to%20resonate%2C%20touching%20something%20deep%20inside%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pahuja%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Federal%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20now%20Oscar-nominated%20film%20documentary%20%E2%80%98To%20Kill%20A%20Tiger%E2%80%99%20was%20released%20in%20September%202022%20and%20has%20been%20screened%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310790%2Fpunjab-satwinder-kaur-abb-nahi-social-welfare-society-helps-abandoned-brides-find-justice%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilm%20festivals%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20world%2C%20receiving%20over%2020%20international%20awards%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20Best%20Canadian%20Film%20at%20the%20Toronto%20International%20Film%20Festival%2C%20the%20Best%20Documentary%20at%20New%20York%20Indian%20Film%20Festival%20and%20Palm%20Springs%20International%20Film%20Festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706103243000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fh1KJF0BMDs8%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D339627%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nominated%20for%20the%20Oscars%2C%20Nisha%20Pahuja's%20documentary%20'To%20Kill%20A%20Tiger'%20is%20about%20a%20father%E2%80%99s%20courageous%20pursuit%20of%20justice%20for%20his%2013-year-old%20daughter.%20Here's%20the%20real%20life%20story%20of%20Jharkhand's%20Ranjit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339627%2Fto-kill-a-tiger-academy-awards-oscars-nominations-2024-jharkhand-ranjit-justice-rape-sexual-assault-pocso%2F%22%