20far%20from%20ordinary.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326801%2Fvedhapriya-ganesan-snake-rescuer-wildlife-conservationist-pet-stylist-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBorn%20in%20Chennai%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20raised%20across%20three%20continents%2C%20the%20world%20was%20really%20her%20oyster.%20The%20national%20level%20swimmer%20started%20swimming%20at%20the%20age%20of%20three.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%201983%20World%20Cup%2C%20inspired%20by%20Sir%20Vivian%20Richards%2C%20she%20also%20started%20playing%20cricket%20at%20four.%20Playing%20for%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20state%20team%20at%20just%20eight%20years%20old%2C%20she%20was%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20under-19%20state%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20sights%20set%20on%20joining%20the%20national%20team%20along%20with%20achieving%20excellence%20in%20academics%2C%20she%20felt%20that%20everything%20was%20going%20her%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20even%20the%20shadow%20of%20failure%20had%20touched%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20everything%20changed%20in%20the%20blink%20of%20an%20eye%20when%20she%20was%2018.%20Enjoying%20with%20her%20friends%20on%20a%20Puducherry%20beach%2C%20she%20suddenly%20fell%20down%20while%20playing%20in%20the%20water.%20A%20spinal%20cord%20injury%20left%20her%20without%20any%20feeling%20under%20the%20neck.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20unwavering%20love%20and%20support%20of%20her%20parents%2C%20and%20her%20incredible%20resilience%2C%20she%20emerged%20like%20a%20phoenix%2C%20and%20today%20provides%20wings%20to%20hundreds%20of%20people%20with%20spinal%20cord%20injury%20through%20her%20venture%20%E2%80%98Soulfree%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20charitable%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoulfree%20INSPIRE%20(Integrated%20Spinal%20Rehabilitation%20Centre)%20in%202013%2C%20the%20trust%E2%80%99s%20rehab%20centre%2C%20provides%20holistic%20treatment%2C%20rehabilitation%2C%20medical%20care%2C%20education%2C%20counselling%2C%20employment%20opportunities%20to%20persons%20with%20spinal%20cord%20injuries%20for%20free.%20The%2020%2C000%20square%20feet%20facility%20in%20Tiruvannamalai%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20has%20helped%20over%20200%20people%20with%20severe%20disabilities%20live%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESwimming%20against%20the%20tide%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201074px)%20100vw%2C%201074px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-12-1705936152.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221074%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Preethi%20has%20helped%20over%202500%20people%20with%20spinal%20cord%20injuries%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-12-1705936152.jpg%201074w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-12-1705936152-300x175.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-12-1705936152-500x292.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-12-1705936152-768x449.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-12-1705936152-150x88.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338800%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPreethi%20has%20helped%20over%202500%20people%20with%20spinal%20cord%20injuries%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20accident%2C%20Preethi%20was%20in%20shock%20and%20faced%20a%20really%20tough%20time.%20From%20excelling%20in%20all%20spheres%20of%20life%2C%20being%20confined%20to%20a%20wheelchair%20broke%20her%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20heart%20was%20totally%20broken.%20I%20had%20a%20privileged%20existence%20for%20the%20first%2018%20years%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20was%20showered%20with%20love%20at%20home%2C%20was%20in%20the%20top%202%20percent%20of%20students%20in%20America%2C%20played%20cricket%20with%20legends%2C%20was%20extremely%20fit%20and%20beautiful.%20I%20was%20making%20my%20way%20towards%20success%2C%20when%20the%20accident%20left%20me%20in%20complete%20shock%2C%E2%80%9D%20Preethi%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20from%20being%20able%20to%20throw%20the%20ball%20with%20full%20force%2C%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20even%20move%20her%20little%20finger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20being%20extraordinary%20in%20every%20way%2C%20I%20suddenly%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20feed%20myself%2C%20bathe%20myself.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20get%20out%20of%20bed.%20It%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337346%2Fdisability-inspiring-veena-ambarish-kari-dosa-food-cart-bengaluru-jp-nagar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereally%20broke%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20parents%20stood%20by%20her%20like%20rocks%20through%20this%20entire%20ordeal.%20Her%20father%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20take%20care%20of%20her%20and%20they%20moved%20to%20Tiruvannamalai%2C%20a%20spiritual%2C%20temple%20town%2C%20to%20heal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreethi%20then%20tried%20to%20get%20admission%20to%20a%20correspondence%20course%20for%20BSc%20Psychology%2C%20but%20she%20was%20rejected%20as%20there%20were%20practical%20classes%20and%20the%20colleges%20were%20not%20disabled-friendly.%20There%20were%20no%20elevators%20or%20ramps.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20remembers%20being%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20do%20people%20like%20you%20come%20to%20study%3F%E2%80%9D%20Her%20father%2C%20her%20biggest%20cheerleader%2C%20bought%20her%20books%20to%20study%2C%20and%20motivated%20her%20to%20educate%20herself%2C%20degree%2C%20or%20no%20degree.%20He%20would%20read%20out%20to%20her%20from%20various%20books%20across%20genres%2C%20from%20fiction%20to%20educational%20books%20to%20spiritual%20books.%20She%20would%20fight%20with%20him%2C%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20go%20of%20her%20hand%2C%20and%20helped%20her%20overcome%20her%20pain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20she%20started%20piecing%20her%20life%20together%2C%20another%20big%20wave%20hit%20her.%20Her%20father%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%20in%202007%2C%20and%20just%20four%20days%20later%2C%20her%20mother%2C%20too%2C%20had%20a%20heart%20attack%20and%20had%20to%20have%20a%20bypass%20surgery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20world%20was%20rocked%20again.%20I%20had%20an%2080-year-old%20grandmother%20to%20take%20care%20of.%20We%20had%20to%20go%20to%20Chennai%20for%20the%20surgery.%20We%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20we%20would%20manage%20the%20next%20meal%20or%20who%20would%20even%20help%20me%20sit%20on%20my%20wheelchair.%20I%20had%20to%20start%20earning%20money%20and%20life%20seemed%20difficult%20all%20over%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Preethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20her%20friends%20reiterated%20the%20need%20for%20her%20to%20get%20a%20formal%20degree.%20She%20took%20up%20BSc%20Medical%20Sociology%20as%20it%20had%20no%20practical%20exams.%20She%20also%20did%20MSc%20in%20Psychology%20despite%20wanting%20to%20do%20counselling%20psychology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20counsel%20people%20as%20my%20voice%20is%20the%20only%20thing%20I%20have.%20I%20was%20denied%20admission%20and%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20psychology%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20too%20deserve%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup