or%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20historian%20Ramachandra%20Guha%20argued%20that%20since%20the%20dawn%20of%20Independence%2C%20there%20are%20only%20a%20few%20Government%20of%20India%20ministers%20who%20%E2%80%9Cshall%20be%20remembered%20for%20having%20carried%20out%20programmes%20that%20radically%20reshaped%20the%20lives%20of%20their%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuha%20listed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F163334%2Fsardar-vallabhbhai-patel-ias-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESardar%20Vallabhai%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20as%20home%20minister%20between%201947%20and%201950%2C%20carried%20out%20the%20integration%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F124500%2Fsardar-patel-vp-menon-integration-princely-states-india-independence%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprincely%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthus%20altering%20the%20politics%20and%20geography%20of%20modern%20India%E2%80%9D.%20Next%2C%20he%20listed%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20who%20as%20finance%20minister%20between%201991%20and%201996%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdismantled%20the%20licence-permit-quota-raj%2C%20thus%20altering%20the%20economy%20and%20society%20of%20modern%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Vallabhai%20Patel%20and%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20Guha%20listed%20the%20name%20of%20Madhu%20Dandavate%20%E2%80%94%20a%20physicist%2C%20freedom%20fighter%2C%20and%20socialist%20leader%20from%20Maharashtra%20%E2%80%94%20who%20as%20railway%20minister%20in%20the%20Janata%20Government%20between%201977%20and%201979%20%E2%80%9Cput%20two%20inches%20of%20foam%20on%20what%20passed%20for%20%E2%80%98reserved%20sleeper%20berths%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20second-class%20sections%20of%20trains%E2%80%9D.%20Although%20a%20simple%20intervention%2C%20this%20initiative%20had%20a%20profound%20influence%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20millions%20of%20ordinary%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Guha%20argued%2C%20%E2%80%9CBefore%201977%20(the%20year%20Dandavate%20became%20railway%20minister)%2C%20there%20was%20an%20enormous%20difference%20between%20the%20first-class%2C%20where%20the%20berths%20were%20padded%2C%20and%20the%20second-class%2C%20where%20they%20were%20made%20of%20hard%20and%20bare%20wood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20were%20lucky%20enough%20to%20travel%20up%20front%2C%20you%20slept%20well%3B%20otherwise%20you%20woke%20up%20with%20a%20painful%20back%20and%20(were%20it%20winter)%20a%20cold%20in%20the%20head%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229283%2Findian-railways-rare-pictures-history-first-train-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Railways%3C%2Fa%3E%20carries%20approximately%2023%20million%20passengers%20daily%20from%20nearly%20all%20strata%20of%20society.%20Dandavate%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20introduce%20these%20two%20inches%20of%20foam%20was%20driven%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20assist%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20poor%20in%20a%20practical%20way.%20As%20he%20once%20famously%20argued%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20want%20to%20do%20is%20not%20degrade%20the%20first%20class%2C%20but%20elevate%20the%20second%20class%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20railway%20minister%20for%20those%20two%20years%2C%20those%20two%20inches%20of%20foam%20were%20put%20in%20place%20across%20the%20major%20trunk%20lines.%20The%20first%20train%20with%20these%20safer%20and%20more%20comfortable%20seats%20was%20flagged%20off%20on%2026%20December%2C%201977%2C%20between%20Mumbai%20and%20Kolkata%20(and%20back).%20Even%20though%20the%20Railway%20Board%20wanted%20to%20call%20this%20train%20the%20Eastern%20Express%2C%20Dandavate%20decided%20on%20the%20name%20Gitanjali%20Express%2C%20inspired%20by%20Rabindranath%20Tagore.%20The%20train%20even%20had%20portraits%20of%20the%20Bengali%20poet%20hung%20inside%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Guha%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20process%20was%20begun%20it%20could%20scarcely%20be%20stopped.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%201980s%2C%20all%20trains%20of%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20had%20these%20padded%20berths%20in%20their%20second-class%20compartments.%20By%20now%20the%20change%20has%20helped%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20people.%20If%20a%20social%20history%20of%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20is%20ever%20written%2C%20it%20might%20be%20divided%20into%20two%20parts%2C%20these%20entitled%20%E2%80%98Life%20before%20Dandavate%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Life%20after%20Dandavate%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20this%20initiative%2C%20he%20also%20introduced%20the%20computerisation%20of%20railway%20reservations%20%E2%80%9Cto%20curb%20corruption%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cstreamline%20the%20procedures%E2%80%9D.%20As%20he%20noted%20in%20his%20Railway%20Budget%20speech%20for%201978-79%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20streamline%20the%20mammoth%20and%20complex%20operation%20involved%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20reservation%20of%20rail%20accommodation%20in%20trains%20and%20to%20eliminate%20malpractices%2C%20I%20am%20also%20considering%20computerisation%20of%20passenger%20reservations%20in%20the%20four%20metropolitan%20cities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20repaired%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20Indian%20Government%20and%20railway%20unions%20that%20had%20suffered%20during%20the%20strike%20of%201974%20and%20was%20suppressed%20by%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20man%20of%20his%20time%20and%20ahead%20of%20his%20time%2C%20Dandavate%20lived%20a%20remarkable%20life%20in%20the%20public%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FMadhu-Dandavate-Image-3-1705674442.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%