f%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263172%2Fmahatma-gandhi-jayanti-best-quotes-inspiring-heroes-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMahatma%20Gandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20issued%20the%20clarion%20call%20for%20%E2%80%98Quit%20India%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20in%20the%20Royal%20Institute%20of%20Science.%20I%20heard%20the%20speech%20delivered%20by%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20at%20the%20Congress%20session%20in%201942.%20I%20was%20in%20college%20when%20the%20call%20given%20to%20the%20people%20was%20%E2%80%98Do%20or%20Die%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20warning%20given%20to%20the%20British%20was%20%E2%80%98Quit%20India%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20the%20Independence%20activist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMahatma%20Gandhi%20wanted%20his%20message%20to%20be%20heard%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20so%20he%20delivered%20his%20speech%20both%20in%20Hindi%20and%20English.%20I%20was%20present%20as%20a%20visitor%20in%20that%20session%20and%20was%20deeply%20moved%20and%20inspired%20by%20its%20proceedings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20Gandhi%2C%20however%2C%20he%20was%20also%20deeply%20inspired%20by%20the%20ideals%20of%20the%20Congress%20Socialist%20Party.%20Its%20leaders%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20likes%20of%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%2C%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%2C%20and%20Yusuf%20Meherally%20%E2%80%94%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20shaping%20his%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Independence%2C%20these%20socialist%20leaders%20quit%20the%20parent%20Congress%20party%2C%20providing%20a%20strong%20and%20principled%20opposition%20to%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%20Dandavate%20followed%20their%20lead%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESatyagraha%20for%20the%20Liberation%20of%20Goa%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Goa%20was%20freed%20from%20the%20clutches%20of%20Portuguese%20colonial%20rule%20and%20joined%20the%20Indian%20union%20only%20on%2019%20December%2C%201961%20(following%20military%20action%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army)%2C%20many%20leaders%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20likes%20of%20Dandavate%20%E2%80%94%20performed%20courageous%20acts%20of%20Satyagraha%20marked%20by%20nonviolent%20protests%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20Indian%20Government%20to%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20secretary%20of%20the%20Goa%20Vimochan%20Sahayak%20Samiti%20(Goa%20Liberation%20Aid%20Committee)%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20he%20bravely%20led%20a%20group%20of%2093%20people%20to%20launch%20a%20Satyagraha%20at%20Netarda%20(a%20small%20village%20on%20the%20border%20of%20Goa)%20and%20paid%20a%20pretty%20heavy%20price%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20wrote%20in%20his%20book%20%E2%80%98Dialogue%20with%20Life%2C%20%E2%80%9CNormally%20when%20the%20Satyagraha%20was%20announced%2C%20the%20police%20were%20posted%20on%20the%20border%2C%20but%20we%20walked%20about%207-8%20miles%20beyond%20the%20Portuguese%20border%2C%20raising%20slogans.%20I%20had%20the%20national%20tricolour%20flag%20in%20my%20hand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Portuguese%20police%20came.%20They%20were%20well-armed.%20We%20were%20stopped.%20I%20was%20in%20the%20front%20and%20was%20asked%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20flag.%20I%20refused%20to%20do%20so.%20We%20had%20come%20here%20to%20hoist%20this%20flag%20in%20the%20Goan%20territory%2C%20and%20I%20would%20not%20surrender%20it.%20They%20beat%20me%20and%20after%20an%20intense%20struggle%2C%20they%20took%20away%20the%20flag.%20We%20were%20asked%20to%20return%20but%20we%20did%20not%20budge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBacked%20by%20slogans%20like%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%98Nahin%2C%20nahin%2C%20Kabhi%20nahin%2C%20Bharat%20Goa%20alag%20nahin%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Lathi%2C%20goli%20khayenge%2C%20phir%20bhi%20Goa%20jayenge%E2%80%99%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehe%20took%20on%20the%20might%20of%20the%20Portuguese%20colonial%20police%20as%20they%20began%20a%20lathi%20charge%20on%20all%20%3Cem%3Esatyagrahis%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20beat%20them%20with%20the%20butts%20of%20their%20rifles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20beat%20me%20till%20I%20fell%20unconscious.%20Strangely%20enough%2C%20even%20after%20I%20became%20unconscious%2C%20they%20trampled%20on%20my%20back%20with%20their%20military%20shoes.%20After%20a%20while%2C%20my%20colleagues%20took%20me%20to%20the%20Military%20Hospital%20at%20Belgaum%20and%20then%20to%20Bombay.%20They%20found%20that%20my%20hip%20joints%20were%20injured%20very%20badly%20and%20I%20had%20to%20be%20given%20infrared%20rays%20for%20that%20injury.%20My%20strong%20young%20bones%20could%20take%20the%20torture%20then%2C%20but%20later%20on%2C%20after%20many%20years%2C%20it%20was%20diagnosed%20that%20my%20hip%20joints%20had%20totally%20degenerated%20and%20the%20replacement%20of%20these%20joints%20with%20metallic%20plates%20and%20rods%20was%20the%20only%20solution.%20At%20present%20I%20have%20two%20stainless%20steel%20plates%20and%20two%20metallic%20rods%20in%20my%20body%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20really%20a%20brutal%20episode%20as%20far%20as%20police%20action%20is%20concerned.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20the%20police%20would%20usually%20just%20arrest%20the%20%3Cem%3Esatyagrahis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20take%20them%20to%20jail.%20But%20the%20%3Cem%3Esatyagrahis%20%3C%2Fem%3Emade%20their%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriting%20on%20the%20impact%20of%20this%20Satyagraha%20action%2C%20he%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20proud%20to%20say%20that%20it%20did%20generate%20a%20climate%20to%20pressurise%20the%20Indian%20Government%20leading%20to%20the%20military%20action%20to%20liberate%20Goa.%20There%20was%20hardly%20any%20resistance%20during%20the%20military%20action.%20My%20feeling%20is%20if%20this%20military%20action%20had%20been%20taken%20earlier%2C%20there%20would%20not%20have%20been%20so%20much%20sacrifice%20and%20death.%20Our%20Satyagraha%20in%201955%20did%20create%20a%20spirit%20of%20resistance%20against%20Portuguese%20rule%20in%20Goa.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20on%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Emergency%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20of%20his%20socialist%20peers%2C%20Dandavate%20challenged%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20administration%E2%80%99s%20proclamation%20of%20Emergency%20(1975%20to%201977)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dark%20period%20in%20our%20history%20marked%20by%20the%20usurping%20of%20basic%20civil%20rights%20and%20democracy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20served%20many%20stints%20in%20prison%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnessing%20the%20inhuman%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20political%20prisoners%2C%20particularly%20his%20colleague%20and%20socialist%20leader%20Mrinal%20Gore%2C%20Dandavate%20shot%20off%20a%20letter%20to%20Indira%20Gandhi%20from%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20quite%20conscious%20of%20the%20consequences%20of%20this%20letter.%20I%20can%20well%20imagine%20that%20through%20this%20communication%2C%20I%20am%20likely%20to%20incur%20your%20wrath%20and%20get%20my%20detention%20prolonged.%20However%2C%20I%20feel%20least%20worried%20about%20it.%20I%20will%20remain%20completely%20undeterred%20even%20if%20the%20prison%20yard%20from%20which%20I%20write%20this%20letter%20were%20to%20become%20my%20graveyard%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Madhu%20Dandavate%20in%20a%20letter%20dated%2014%20January%2C%201976%2C%20to%20the%20then%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20during%20the%20Emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20signed%20off%20this%20scathing%20letter%20to%20the%20then-prime%20minister%20by%20declaring%20his%20undying%20will%20to%20resist.%20%E2%80%9CRest%20assured%20that%20in%20this%20land%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20my%20will%20to%20fight%20for%20freedom%20will%20ever%20remain%20more%20powerful%20than%20the%20engine%20of%20repression%20that%20seeks%20to%20suppress%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDandavate%2C%20however%2C%20is%20also%20famously%20known%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww